ed seg skattefradraget.", "- Du kan fritt reinvestere i nye aksjer eller fond, men hvis du \u00f8nsker \u00e5 fortsette \u00e5 spare i den samme aksjen/fondet som du sitter med tap p\u00e5, og realiserer beholdningen kun for \u00e5 f\u00e5 fradraget, b\u00f8r du v\u00e6re klar over at skattemyndighetene kan gripe inn, sier Magnussen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|okonomi"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "bce0c99164478f3f563ac8b8c8fa2d2df1cb41884f2e32006c4cee071d695bd3"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-28T22:43:38.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Har du fond eller aksjer som g\u00e5r i minus? Da kan staten dekke deler av tapet ditt."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article6815829.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/OysteinMagnussen.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/cda4457fcac773ce010cf252168729f78c0ce1f2.jpg?5903c59a"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Kvitt deg med d\u00e5rlige fond f\u00f8r nytt\u00e5r -adressa.no", "- Napp ut gr\u00e5 h\u00e5r", "Advarer mot skattetriks"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "cda4457fcac773ce010cf252168729f78c0ce1f2"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["\u00f8konomi", "finans", "aksjer", "skatt", "b\u00f8rs", "\u00f8konominyheter"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "\u00f8konomi,finans,aksjer,skatt,b\u00f8rs,\u00f8konominyheter"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "okonomi"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "personal-finance"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["aksjer", "gr\u00e5 h\u00e5r", "d\u00e5rlige fond", "fond"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "markets trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "\u00f8ystein magnussen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["n